(That will be a little difficult there Cyberwolf)

Ice::
"I know.  I still feel like a maximal inside. The basic principals 
and values still mean something to me. I don't know why, but they 
do." She looked down and sighed. "Honor, goodness, valor, humility, 
honesty, caring for others, forgiveness. These things still hold to 
me. I can't help it."

She heard Veratis. Sighs,"Well, we can spar later on I guess." She 
hung her head and walked back into the base. She kept her mind 
closed. She didn't want to know what Lunarpine was thinking right 
then.
